{"tid":1065120,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Mayday] Webm to mp4","createTime":"2019-03-17T04:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T12:43:42.000Z","uid":101587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25c248ded1100af36e455f5a5e3e93024ba48858","tid":1065120,"uid":101587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"小弟想整片,但錄左webm format, 我用 vegas pro 14 整片, 但vegas pro read唔倒 webm, 所以用VLC Player轉 webm做 mp4, 但我試過轉做 Video - H.264 + mp3既話, 入落vegas pro 14就得聲, 然後轉做 Video - H.265 + mp3既話, 入落vegas pro 14就得畫面, 想問仲有無d 方法可以好快咁將大量 webm format 轉做 mp4 而 vegas pro 14 係聲音畫面都睇倒? Thanks~"},{"pid":"42384bfbd4221cc3e6c3951b077763eacae6b76d","tid":1065120,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"ffmpeg -i video.webm -vcodec libx264 -acodec libmp3lame video.mp4<br />\n收錢既軟件&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9e006562c06bf9fb58d59e4db58339f6ed24a415","tid":1065120,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"<code>find ./ -name '*.webm' -exec bash -c 'ffmpeg -i $0 -c:v libx264 -qp 0 -preset veryfast -c:a libopus -f mp4 ${0/webm/mp4}' {} \\;</code><br />\n唔係 lossless<br />\n利申: 未試過"},{"pid":"7c30fd96f656f391b7a09bf92b4b31be9a2c5607","tid":1065120,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42384bfbd4221cc3e6c3951b077763eacae6b76d","tid":1065120,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"ffmpeg -i video.webm -vcodec libx264 -acodec libmp3lame video.mp4<br />\n收錢既軟件&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"家陣咩年代呀仲用 -vcodec -acodec <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2671fcba24d7ecce0e33ed9f7b0111aa1f3e2a48","tid":1065120,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c30fd96f656f391b7a09bf92b4b31be9a2c5607","tid":1065120,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42384bfbd4221cc3e6c3951b077763eacae6b76d","tid":1065120,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"ffmpeg -i video.webm -vcodec libx264 -acodec libmp3lame video.mp4<br />\n收錢既軟件&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"家陣咩年代呀仲用 -vcodec -acodec <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"咩年代唔可以用 -vcodec -acodec ?"}]}